{"tid":843706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁都得】河南教堂辦佛教儀式 網民：褻瀆意圖","createTime":"2018-10-01T10:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T11:40:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d6696c1cb24f7db68466ab4709700dd8b41252","tid":843706,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538383990_a777.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538383990_a777.jpg&h=009a557d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梵蒂岡早前與中國簽訂任命主教臨時協議。外界關注內地教徒受打壓的情況，將會改善還是惡化。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電視於官方twitter貼出一段有指於河南拍攝的影片，指當地一家天主教堂，內外被拆除十字架後，當局更周日安排佛教徒在教堂內進行佛教儀式。影片所見，有僧侶在教堂內誦經，現場亦有其他和尚和信徒。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指，這是打壓天主教和基督教的最新方式，不但有褻瀆意圖，還製造各宗教之間的矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181001/58744353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58744353&d=wxCBMOCrh%2F4zoxv4IeR4H6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=2912a126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58744353&h=725a03ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181001/58744353</a>"},{"pid":"c347807e5ac74f98294ae33af8cc639e72eb8c7b","tid":843706,"uid":36178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"我想睇係天主教堂破地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38adb3816bde9d2f8ad6e5fc66ba07a6956c299a","tid":843706,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一堂多教"},{"pid":"8a022e5a4d9276c6d7d7de8c497d44310aed04ac","tid":843706,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cited